idea-plugin.description:
这个插件可以将Java文件的全局字段排序，按代码的长度由短到长排序。
idea会自动根据属性的修饰符分组，很遗憾，目前无法改变。
This plug-in can sort the global fields of Java files, from short to long,
according to the length of the code.
Idea is automatically grouped according to the modifier of the attribute,
which unfortunately cannot be changed at this time.
For example:
int i;
@Resource
Service service;
boolean bool;

After handle:
int i;
boolean bool;
@Resource
Service service;

idea-plugin.change-notes:
